            <title>[FLINK-17805] InputProcessorUtil doesn&apos;t handle indexes for multiple inputs operators correctly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-17805</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
